  <brief_title>A Phase 1 Single-Dose Escalation Study of PF-04308515 in Healthy Volunteers</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Phase 1, Randomized, Double-Blind, Sponsor-Open, Placebo-Controlled, Single-Dose Escalation Trial Evaluating the Safety, Tolerability, Pharmacokinetics and Pharmacodynamics of PF-04308515 in Healthy Volunteers</official_title>
