  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to determine the safety, tolerability, pharmacokinetics
      (understanding how a drug is absorbed and moves through the body) and pharmacodynamics
      (understanding the effects of a drug on certain target sites of activity in the body).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
